 Ms Phiri, who prides herself in keeping the Middelburg Mall spotless, was contacted by other staff members and was told that a shopper was unwell.
Having first aid training under her belt, Sibongile hurried to Pep to find a woman in labour. Like a superwoman, Sibongile took charge of the situation where she settled the mother down in a storeroom and helped her through contractions.
